descriptionHtml:
Check your Assam HSLC result and AHSEC results 2021 just like cybercafes for free at your own home. Use this app on your phone and you will be able to check your result just after they have been released by the Assam Board. Checking news and any updates related to the HSLC & AHSEC exam is simply easy and fun by using this app. App is built in a way so that you can get your result instant without being in the line of cyber cafe.


How to use this App? 


1) Open the App on your mobile


2) Click on your Class (10th result 2021/ 12th result 2021)


3) Click on CHECK RESULT NOW


4) Provide your ROLL CODE & ROLL NUMBER


5) Now click on Check now


6) HSLC & AHSEC Result 2021


Hurray! Your result is in front of you. After checking your result you can save it into PDF or you can send them to your friends and families by using Whatsapp or any sharing app.

- Checking your Assam HSLC/AHSEC 2021 result


- Latest Exam Updates
